OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy, with
OL,6,Frain spreading eastwards during the
OL,7,Fevening, perhaps with some heavier
OL,8,Fbursts. Mostly dry by dawn, with a few
OL,9,Fclear spells. Becoming breezy again
OL,10,Flater in the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FOften cloudy and mostly dry,
OL,13,Falthough some drizzly outbreaks are
OL,14,Fpossible, mostly on western hills.
OL,15,FSome brighter spells, mainly for
OL,16,Feastern parts. Breezy, with strong
OL,17,Fgusts over high ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
