OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand mild with occasional rain
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday. Some drier,
OL,8,Fbrighter spells, especially in the
OL,9,Feast. Winds strengthening Thursday.
OL,10,FOvernight rain clearing early Friday,
OL,11,Fthen cooler with blustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
